---
Egomancers are offensive psionic casters specializing in weaponized cognition and mental domination.
They emerged from the Assertion Wing of the Psionicist tradition, which was expelled from the mainstream academies.
Core philosophy: the mind's primary power lies in imposition, overriding external cognitive processes through focused intent.
Combat role is sustained mental pressure against opponents, favoring continuous disruption over single decisive bursts.
Key abilities include attention redirection, concentration disruption, decision-making override, and awareness fragmentation.
The tradition requires continuous modeling of the target's cognitive state while delivering intervention.
Training occurs in independent schools outside the Violet Compact's registry.
This is a remort class for Psionicists who commit to the imposition doctrine.
Effects target the opponent's cognitive architecture rather than observable physical reality.
The Kinetimancer class builds on Egomancer psionic methodology combined with Necromancer entropy knowledge.
